tags.name: docx-file-system-broker
tags.description:
Web component that bridges local file system via File API and
combines the functionality of the DOCX parser so that you can easily
load a file / directory from the user's file system and then access
that data from DOCX

Events:

  * `docx-reader-ready` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - 

  * `docx-file-system-data` {`CustomEvent<{ name: any; value: any; }>`} - 

Properties:

  * `libPath` {`string`} - 

  * `dirHandler` - 

  * `fileHandler` - 

  * `files` {`never[]`} -

tags.name: xlsx-file-system-broker
tags.description:
Web component that bridges local file system via File API and
combines the functionality of the XSLX parser so that you can easily
load a file / directory from the user's file system and then access
that data from XLSX / ODS / CSV repos

Events:

  * `xlsx-ready` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - 

  * `xlsx-file-system-data` {`CustomEvent<{ filename: string; format: any; operation: string; data: string; }>`} - 

Properties:

  * `XLSX` - 

  * `libPath` {`string`} - 

  * `XW` - 

  * `dirHandler` - 

  * `fileHandler` - 

  * `files` {`never[]`} -
